<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٦٠٤)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ رَجُلٌ مِنْ بَنِي تَمِيمٍ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١ - إنْ تُنَصِفُونَا آلَ مَرْوَانَ نَقْتَرِبْ ... إلَيْكُمْ وَإلاَّ فَأْذَنوا بِبِعَادِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢ - فَإِنَّ لَنَا عَنْكُمْ مَزَاحاً وَمَرْحَلاً ... بِعِيسٍ إِلَى رِيحِ الْفَلاةِ صَوَادِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٣ - وَفِي الأَرْضِ عَنْ دَارِ الْقِلَى مُتَحَوَّلٌ ... وَكُلُّ بِلادٍ أُوطِنَتْ كَبلادِي<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٦٠٥)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عُبَيْدُ اللَّهِ بْنُ الْحُرِّ الْجُعْفِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>١ - فَإِنْ تَجْفُ عَنِّي أَوْ تُرِدْ لِي إِهَانَةً ... أجِدْ عَنْكَ فِي الأَرْضِ الْعَريضَةِ مَذْهَبَا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٢ - فَلا تَحْسِبَنَّ الأَرْضَ بَاباً سَدَدْتَهُ ... عَلَىَّ وَلا الْمِصْرَيْنِ أُمًّا وَلا أَبَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٦٠٦)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ سَلَمَةُ بْنُ زَيْدِ الْبَجَلِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الكامل)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>١ - لا خَيْرَ فِي بَلَدٍ يُضَامُ عَزِيزُهُ ... وَعَنِ الْهَوَانِ مَذَاهِبٌ وَمَنَادِحُ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٦٠٧)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عُبَيْدُ اللَّهِ بْنُ الْحُرِّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>